Class RecvPacket

java.lang.Object
  flightsim.simconnect.recv.RecvPacket
Direct Known Subclasses:

public class RecvPacket
extends java.lang.Object

Base class for all received data packets. It contains structural information about the packet, such as simConnect protocol version.

lc0277
